OL,7,FA driver who was filmed skidding his
OL,8,Fcar and driving at high speeds around
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Sheppey has been jailed.
OL,11,FFootage found on George Ivers' phone
OL,12,Fshowed him doing doughnut manoeuvres
OL,13,Fnear the Sheppey Crossing and speeding
OL,14,Fthrough the centre of Sheerness.
OL,16,FThe videos were filmed in late 2021
OL,17,Fand early 2022 and were found by
OL,18,Fdetectives investigating a fatal
OL,19,Fcollision involving a cyclist in Lower
OL,20,FRoad, Teynham in the early hours of 2
OL,21,FMay 2022.
