OL,7,FThe cyclist, a 19 year old man,
OL,8,Fsuffered catastrophic injuries and
OL,9,Fdied at the scene.
OL,11,FWork by roads policing officers
OL,12,Fidentified Ivers' VW Polo as the car
OL,13,Finvolved and he was arrested later the
OL,14,Fsame morning.
OL,16,FHe had driven the heavily-damaged car
OL,17,Fafter the collision, before removing
OL,18,Fany documents linking him to the
OL,19,Fvehicle and abandoning it in Sheerness.
